NAME: Disappearing community invite message 1:1 @ios @low-risk @2-devices

DESCRIPTION: Verifies that a link preview disappears as expected in a 1:1 conversation
NAME: Disappearing link message 1:1 @ios @low-risk @2-devices

DESCRIPTION: Verifies that a GIF disappears as expected in a 1:1 conversation
NAME: Disappearing GIF message 1:1 @ios @low-risk @2-devices

Verifies that an image can be sent to a community.

NAME: Avatar color @ios @medium-risk @2-devices
